File Dialog Tool
----------------
File Dialog Tool is an activity which alows browsing the file system of your
device and pick file paths for loading or saving data.

![Browsing.](2.png)

![When called with 'save- file' option, a floatig action button to do so is displayed. Argument returned will show if just the folder or folder and file was picked.](3.png)

![Preview feature.](1.png)

